#include <stdio.h>

int main (void)

{

int i, sum;

for (i = 1, sum = 0; i <= 10; i++)

{

sum += i; #ifdef DEBUG

printf ("sum += %d is %d\n", i, sum); #endif

}

printf ("total sum is %d\n", sum);

return 0;

}
